  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You have absolute control and understanding of your attunement with the stellar forces of the cosmos. If you would become graviton or photon-attuned, you instead become perfectly-attuned. When you are perfectly-attuned, you can choose which attunement bonus to benefit from (either graviton or photon-attuned) when using any of your abilities. If any of your abilities require you to be in a specific attunement state, being perfectly-attuned counts as your choice of graviton or photon-attuned.</p>"
